## Septic Systems in Orlando

Orlando's flat terrain and sandy soil provide generally good conditions for septic systems, though high water tables in some areas require careful planning.

### Local Regulations

Orange County Health Department regulates septic systems. Proper permits and inspections are required for all major work.
